com.interpss.core.algo.dclf

Interface SenAnalysisAlgorithm

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, DclfAlgorithm, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, IBranchAngleShiftFactor, IDclfAlgoLookup, IDclfResult, IGenTDFactor, ILineOutageDFactor, IPowerTDFactor, ISensitivity, NameTag, NetworkRef<BaseAclfNetwork<?,?>>, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ContingencyAnalysisAlgorithm, NetGenAdjustAlgorithm
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ContingencyAnalysisAlgorithmImpl, NetGenAdjustAlgorithmImpl, SenAnalysisAlgorithmImpl

    public interface SenAnalysisAlgorithm
extends DclfAlgorithm, ISensitivity, IGenTDFactor, IPowerTDFactor, ILineOutageDFactor, IBranchAngleShiftFactor
    A representation of the model object 'Algorithm'. Sensitivity analysis algorithm definition. It contains a list of InjectBus and a list of withdrawBus. It implements BusSensitivity, GenPTDF, PTDF, LODF, BranchAngleShiftFactor, interfaces.

    The following features are supported:

    • Withdraw Bus List
    • Inject Bus List
    See Also:
    DclfAlgorithmPackage.getSenAnalysisAlgorithm()
